timelineItems.desc: Attempt saved. Alvaro Saborio (Real Salt Lake) right footed shot from the left side of the box is saved in the bottom left corner.
timelineItems.title: SAVE: Jaime Penedo comes up huge against Alvaro Saborio

timelineItems.name: Travis
timelineItems.text: RSL deserves a goal here with the record amount of shots they have this game. #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: LAG Confidential
timelineItems.text: Great little run by Jamieson. Typical oops a daisy by Leo. #LAGalaxy #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Little MLS Blog
timelineItems.text: Arena is looking toward Saturday’s match with his subs. Does he regret resting starters at home yet? #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Jake Hatch
timelineItems.text: #RSL has been repeatedly denied on the doorstep tonight. The squad looks loads better tonight than they have in quite a while.

timelineItems.name: Dog and Deuce
timelineItems.text: Saborio is working so hard this match, he is a man on a mission. Needs some support from Garcia in last 13mins plus stoppage time.#RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Jeremy Horton
timelineItems.text: 7' #RSL with three offsides in the first 7. With a little more care, eventually they'll get a 1v1 on one of those through balls.

timelineItems.name: Jon Christensen
timelineItems.text: Feels like the pressure is building for #RSL's first real goal in like a month. 80' #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Prost Amerika
timelineItems.text: Olmes Garcia has injected some urgency for @RSL. Should he have come on earlier? #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Derek Paulson
timelineItems.text: Really need a winner here. Keep the pressure up and snag all three points #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Jake Hatch
timelineItems.text: Games like tonight are why Alvaro Saborio is the best forward @RealSaltLake has on their roster. He does the little things so well. #RSL

timelineItems.name: Jake Hatch
timelineItems.text: Sabo's come about as close as you can tonight. Don't get why he takes the rap for "not scoring enough." #RSL https://t.co/8C0FDxes8P

timelineItems.name: Marco Delgado
timelineItems.text: Great skill from Juninho #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Tommy Fresh
timelineItems.text: Regardless of the result, no concerns with a lack of effort tonight. This has been a fun game to watch #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: kyleewoyote
timelineItems.text: Jordan Allen is a phenomenal talent. Having a heckuva game showing ball control and a crazy good skill set. #RSLvLA

timelineItems.desc: Penalty LA Galaxy. Omar Gonzalez draws a foul in the penalty area.
timelineItems.title: PK SAVE: Rimando dives to deny Junhino from the spot

timelineItems.desc: Penalty conceded by Jamison Olave (Real Salt Lake) after a foul in the penalty area.
timelineItems.title: PENALTY: Jamison Olave concedes the spot kick with a foul on Omar Gonzalez

timelineItems.name: Hopeless Wanderer
timelineItems.text: Sometimes I just don't like seeing Husidic on the field, he's too slow and way too complacent. #LAGalaxy

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray
timelineItems.text: Good look from Philips to swing a ball into Gil but there's too much on the pass and penedo collects. #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: LAG Confidential
timelineItems.text: Zardes should have started that run sooner and he'd be off. Sigh. #LAGalaxy #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Andrew Lord
timelineItems.text: This intricate play from the likes of Gil, Allen, Sabo, Beltran and Saucedo is a VERY bright light. Future is looking good for #RSL.

timelineItems.name: #TeamAsher
timelineItems.text: Olave lucky not to get a second yellow here #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Matt Pollard
timelineItems.text: RSL defender pulls Omar down. Omar possibly goes down easy, but the tug is a foul. #LAGalaxy #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Brett
timelineItems.text: That was an easy penalty call and Rimando saves the day. #RSL

timelineItems.name: Andy Edwards
timelineItems.text: This game is 100% full of #FAIL everywhere you look. #RSLvLA

timelineItems.name: Don Eisenbarth
timelineItems.text: I will never get over Rimando's ability to stop PKs. #Unreal #RSL

timelineItems.name: Royal Review
timelineItems.text: How long has it been now since #RSL scored a goal (read: not given an own goal)? Feels like a pretty ridiculous streak right now.
